      "description": "Offering a pristine example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical integrity. The rear subframe has been reinforced to eliminate common floor-pan fatigue. The chassis retains its factory-spec suspension geometry, paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Every bushing and seal is intact, maintaining original damping characteristics and steering feedback. This is a mechanically transparent, collector-grade vehicle for the purist who demands an unadulterated analog driving experience.",
